          "message": "GWT within influence zone (D_w < D_f + B): full buoyant correction required for γ in N_γ term — EC7 §6.5.3(4) applies"
        },
        {
          "id": "W4",
          "severity": "WARNING",
          "source": "Terzaghi (1943) / Meyerhof (1963/1976)",
